'''Hammer Group''' was a [[Squadron/Legends|squadron]] of [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] that was assigned to the warship ''[[Ralroost]]''. It aided in the [[Battle of Garqi|rescue]] of [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]], [[Ganner Rhysode]], and [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] from [[Garqi/Legends|Garqi]].

